text:
Yeah...
Juri, your shoulders are getting wet.

This umbrella is indeed too small for both of us.
Let's move a little closer.

...Here, take this handkerchief.
Let me wipe it for you, so stay still.

I-It's fine!
I can do it myself...!

No, you'll catch a cold.
Come on, don't move...

...Oh, Juri, look...
The sky over there is already brightening up.

Hehe... I'm sure
this place will clear up soon too.
